								Students should be logging on to their PowerSchool accounts for access of their class schedules. If you have any questions regarding your PowerSchool account please email Mrs. Dunbar at kim.dunbar@lasmontanashigh.com or Mr. Ahner at e.ahner@lasmontanashigh.com. Thank You!
							</p>
						</section></article><article id="hp_news_article_3" class="cf" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Article"><header class="cf"><h1 class="title" itemprop="name headline" id="hp_news_article_3_title">
