							</a>
						</h1>
					</header><section class="summary cf" itemprop="description" aria-labelledby="hp_news_article_4_title"><p>
								Some teachers and staff from the school will be calling all students and parents/guardians on Monday, March 30 to check-in with families and provide important updates. Please answer phone calls you receive from the school number, or an unknown/private number on Monday, March 30 as it will likely be us. We look forward to speaking with you. - Mr. Martinez
							</p>
